No.—. Original.

Ex parte: In the Matter of J. Wesley Glasgow, Petitioner. Motion for leave to file a petition for a writ of habeas corpus. Submitted October 23, 1911. Decided October 30, 1911. Mr. John C. Fay for the petitioner. Per Curiam.

Denied. Ex parte Mirzan, 119 U. S. 584; Riggins v. United States, 199 U. S. 547; In re Lincoln, 202 U. S. 178.
